  Scenario: TC_S04 - SIM Amendments History Tab end-to-end regression

    # ── Edit simFoundArea on G17202130 → verify History entry created ─────────
    When the staff user opens SIM parcel "G17202130", sets simFoundArea to "4" and saves
    Then a new activity entry should be present in the History tab

