    When the staff user navigates back to SIM and opens parcel "G22814025", sets amendedClaimedArea to "6" and saves
    Then a new activity entry should be present in the History tab

    # ── Toggle simIndicator on G22813057 → verify History entry created ───────
    When the staff user navigates back to SIM and opens parcel "G22813057", toggles the SIM indicator and saves
    Then a new activity entry should be present in the History tab

