    And a new activity entry should be present in the History tab after the opt-out

    # ── Toggle SIM back on → verify History entry created ────────────────────
    When the staff user navigates back to SIM and opts SIM back in
    Then a new activity entry should be present in the History tab

    # ── Revert SIM, restore G22813057 indicator and re-submit ────────────────
    When the staff user navigates back to SIM and reverts the SIM changes
    And the staff user opens parcel "G22813057", restores the SIM indicator and saves
    And the staff user submits SIM with notes "Set for Test 7678"
    Then the SIM flow is complete and the application is in its restored state


